      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "DAS层放Raw Tables，有58张表；DAB层放HOOK Frames，也是58个；DAR_Staging层有两个部分：Puppini Bridges 58个，还有Event Bridges 58个；DAR层是Puppini Bridge Union 1个，加上Peripheral Tables 58个。",
